<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About - BurnLink</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: #f2f4f7;
    }
    .card {
      width: min(620px, 92vw);
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }
    .links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #475467;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card">
    <h1>About BurnLink</h1>
    <p>BurnLink is a one-time file sharing app with browser-side end-to-end encryption.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Files are encrypted in your browser before upload.</li>
      <li>Server stores encrypted payload only.</li>
      <li>Links are burned after first successful data fetch.</li>
      <li>Password-protected files lock for 10 minutes after 3 wrong attempts.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
      Developer: <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Joy G. Majumdar</a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
